            "title": "1個月拆息跌至2.34厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15680872&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">香港銀行公會公布的最新香港銀行同業拆息 (HIBOR)，與按揭利率相關的一個月拆息報2.34238厘，創1個月新低。<br/> <br/>   隔夜拆息報1.91393厘，跌2.655基點 ;1星期拆息2.28036厘，跌9.78基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1個月拆息2.34238厘， 跌9.714基點 ; 3個月拆息2.58887厘，跌5基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6個月拆息2.8厘，無升跌 ; 12個月拆息2.88649厘，跌0.518基點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以H按利率H+1.3厘計算，即3.64厘，貸款400萬，年期30年計算，每月供款18276元，但封頂息為3.25厘至3.5厘，即每月供款17408元至17962元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15680872-1%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e8%b7%8c%e8%87%b32-34%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20231205_FI_source_licensed_HK-bank_shutterstock_704.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-28 13:15:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "ADR低水140點   滙控低1.1%  夜期跌143點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR較恆指周五收市低140點或0.53%，報26490點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_HSBC-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/bplib_20230703-172008__source-web_HSBC-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報145.74元，較香港收市價低1.1%，推低恒指29點 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣140.91元，較香港收市價低1.4%，影響恒指26點 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣513.92元，較香港收市價低0.8% ; 影響恒指13點 。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣421.85元，較香港收市價高0.3%， 貢獻恒指5點 ; 友邦保險(01299)ADR收市折合港幣86.38元，較香港收市價低0.5% ; 中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣67.7元，較香港收市價低0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣34.51元，較香港收市價低1.1% ; 百度(09888)ADR收市折合港幣121.67元，較香港收市價低1.6%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報26465點，跌143點，較昨日恒指收市26630點，低水166點，成交18840張。國指夜市期指收報8827點，較昨日國指收市低水32點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15693640-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4140%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e4%bd%8e1-1-%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c143%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-28 13:15:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美元指數變動不大　美國10年期債息失守4厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15693169&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國1月最終需求生產物價指數按月升0.5%，超出預期，美元指數一度升約0.1%，較早時變動不大，較早時報97.666。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美元兌日圓較早時下跌0.1%至155.95日圓。歐元兌美元上升0.18%至1.1818美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英鎊兌美元接近持平在1.3478美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，中東局勢緊張，加上對人工智能的擔憂，推升避險需求，美國國債價格上升，收益率下跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國10年期債息失守4厘水平，是去年11月底以來首次，較早時跌5.5個基點至3.962厘。30年期國債收益率亦跌至4個月新點，報4.632厘，下跌3.2個基點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15693169-%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b10%e5%b9%b4%e6%9c%9f%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%884%e5%8e%98-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240410_source-licensed_USD_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-28 13:01:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金價升1%或以上　地緣政治局勢緊張資金流入避險",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15693171&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價升1%或以上，美伊局勢緊張，資金流入避險。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">現貨金較早時報每盎司5262.6美元，上升1.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4月紐約期金收報每盎司5247.9美元，上升1%。</p>\n</div>",
